channel.description:
magnet:?xt=urn:btih:e45563786033527770ffb992b336ea4afb9190b1&dn=moparcraft%5Flast%5Fmultiworld&tr=udp%3A%2F%2Ftracker.publicbt.com%3A80&tr=udp%3A%2F%2Ftracker.ccc.de%3A80
http://www.moparcraft.net/downloads/moparcraft_last_multiworld.torrent
Enjoy! I'll be uploading at at least 300kbps, if you only want a single map, you can pick and choose which files you want to download or not, but please seed at least what you download. Thanks!
Explanation of files: bukkit.7z - craftbukkit jar and all the plugins/configuration so you can run it as a server just like when we shut it down moparcraft*.7z - World 2 and friends, seed was 'moparcraft' moparscape*.7z - World 1 and friends, seed was 'moparscape' creative.7z - Creative world If you extract all of the above into the same folder and run craftbukkit.jar, the server will be up and ready for you to play with an old client.
.7z files are compressed with 7zip, which is open source and free to download and use here: http://www.7-zip.org/download.html (as if you couldn't have simply [url=https://www.google.com/search?q=.7z+file]google'd ".7z file"[/url])
